com.akiban.sql.parser

Interface NodeNames


  • public interface NodeNames
    This is the set of constants used to identify the classes that are used in NodeFactoryImpl. This class is not shipped. The names are used in NodeFactoryImpl, mapped from int NodeTypes and used in Class.forName calls. WARNING: WHEN ADDING NODE TYPES HERE, YOU MUST ALSO ADD THEM TO tools/jar/DBMSnodes.properties
